"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-pieter-coetze-bronze-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport ByWesley Botton Chief sports journalist 3 minute read 19 February 2024 10:02 am Backstroke swimmer Pieter Coetze on the podium at the World Aquatics Championships in Doha.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 97, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Backstroke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Backstroke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Backstroke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Backstroke\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4128188863267545e-14, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3 minute\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Aquatics Championships\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 173}, {\"ngram\": \"Doha\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Sebastien Bozon/AFP Despite returning home with only one medal from his three individual events, Olympic podium prospect Pieter Coetze says the lessons he has taken from his campaign at theWorld Aquatics Championshipsin Doha will help him fine-tune for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4128188863267545e-14, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sebastien Bozon/AFP\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"only one medal\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"his three individual events\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic podium prospect Pieter Coetze\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"the lessons\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"his campaign\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"fine-tune\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coetzeearned bronze in the men's 200m backstrokein the Qatari capital last week.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coetzeearned bronze\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200m\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"the Qatari capital\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 19-year-old backstroke specialist also finished fourth in the 50m final and grabbed fifth spot in the 100m event.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 19-year-old backstroke specialist\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50m\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"fifth spot\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m event\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The World Aquatics Championships has never been held during an Olympic year, however, and Coetze said he wasn't too concerned about his results as he was entirely focused on the multi-sport showpiece in July.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The World Aquatics Championships\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic year\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"Coetze\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"his results\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"the multi-sport showpiece\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though the Olympic swimming programme would not include a 50m backstroke race, he was set to be among the nation's best medal hopes in Paris, turning out in the 100m and 200m backstroke events and potentially the 4x100m medley relay.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997075458823, \"rank\": 2.9245427266313906e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2615737514208304e-18, \"text\": \"4x100m medley relay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swimming_at_the_2004_Summer_Paralympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic swimming programme\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"a 50m backstroke race\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's best medal hopes\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"200m backstroke events\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With five months to go before the Games, Coetze said he would head back to the training pool and continue preparing for the quadrennial spectacle.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five months\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"Coetze\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the training pool\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"the quadrennial spectacle\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This (World Championships) was always just going to be a preparation competition for [the Olympics],\\\" said the rising teenage star, who earned the national squad's only medal last week.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(World Championships\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"a preparation competition\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"[the Olympics\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"the rising teenage star\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"the national squad's only medal\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's very early in the year.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Normally at this time of year, I am not racing, just training.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's definitely something new for my body that I wasn't used to.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The whole SA team is not used to that so I think we are all very excited for the next few months and hopefully we can peak at the right time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999781746774962, \"rank\": 1.9605491191815194e-05, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next few months\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former world junior champion, who bagged three medals at the2022 Commonwealth Games, said he could take a lot of value from his experience in Doha (aside from his first senior world championship medal) in the build-up to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9995226488583738, \"rank\": 0.0003225272521811173, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1904, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4128188863267545e-14, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The former world junior champion\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"three medals\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"value\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"his experience\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"his first senior world championship medal\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the mental side, I have learnt what state I should be in, what expectations I should and should not have, mostly those kinds of things,\\\" Coetze said.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mental side\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"what state\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"what expectations\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"mostly those kinds\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"Coetze\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And in the pool, there are a few things where I have realised my weaknesses that I need to work on.\\\"\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"a few things\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"my weaknesses\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9957802546622262, \"rank\": 0.004237381279870204, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2373, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Citizen\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"a Preferred Source\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"our trusted reporting\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"Top Stories\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 240